{
  "texts": [
    "Pred, prediction; ref, reference.",
    "TRIPOD 22 and STARD 23), we built the validation of our framework on three main pillars: (1) Delphi processes to challenge and refine the proposals of the expert groups that worked on individual components of the framework; (2) community feedback obtained by broadcasting the framework via society mailing lists and social media platforms; and",
    "(3) and instantiation of the framework to a range of different biological and medical use cases.",
    "Involving and educating users: Choosing adequate validation metrics is a complex process.",
    "Rather than providing a black box recommendation, Metrics Reloaded guides the user through the process of metric selection while raising awareness on pitfalls that may occur."
  ]
}